{"tha-ap292:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap292:0.2":"Pannadayakavagga ","tha-ap292:0.3":"10 Pubbangamiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap292:1.1":"“Cullasitisahassani, ","tha-ap292:1.2":"pabbajimha akincana; ","tha-ap292:1.3":"Tesam pubbangamo asim, ","tha-ap292:1.4":"uttamatthassa pattiya. ","tha-ap292:2.1":"Saraga sabhava cete, ","tha-ap292:2.2":"vippasannamanavila; ","tha-ap292:2.3":"Upatthahimsu sakkaccam, ","tha-ap292:2.4":"pasanna sehi panibhi. ","tha-ap292:3.1":"Khinasava vantadosa, ","tha-ap292:3.2":"katakicca anasava; ","tha-ap292:3.3":"Pharimsu mettacittena, ","tha-ap292:3.4":"sayambhu aparajita. ","tha-ap292:4.1":"Tesam upatthahitvana, ","tha-ap292:4.2":"sambuddhanam patissato; ","tha-ap292:4.3":"Marananca anuppatto, ","tha-ap292:4.4":"devattanca agamhase. ","tha-ap292:5.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap292:5.2":"yam silamanupalayim; ","tha-ap292:5.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap292:5.4":"sannamassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap292:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap292:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap292:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap292:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma pubbangamiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap292:8.1":"Pubbangamiyattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap292:9.1":"Pannadayakavaggo ekunatimsatimo. ","tha-ap292:10.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap292:11.1":"Pannam phalam paccuggamam, ","tha-ap292:11.2":"ekapupphi ca maghava; ","tha-ap292:11.3":"Upatthakapadananca, ","tha-ap292:11.4":"pabbajja buddhupatthako; ","tha-ap292:11.5":"Pubbangamo ca gathayo, ","tha-ap292:11.6":"atthatalisa kittita. "}